{"lastModified":1760356236407,"uri":"c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca299-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nMiren is a beautiful Ferretti 68' totally refitted in 2021/2022! The salon area is cozy, with grey and cream colors, creating a nice atmosphere. She can comfortably accommodate up to eight guests in one Master cabin, one VIP, one Twin with two single beds convertible to double and one Twin cabin with upper and lower berths. She presents many spaces perfect for relaxation and alfresco dining both at the aft deck and at the sundeck. Guests can also enjoy breathtaking views and sunbathe both at the bow area and at the swim platform with the two sun loungers available. The water toys onboard Miren are plenty including a SeaBob!! Her experienced, all year round crew of four will take great care of the guests and will offer them an unforgettable charter experience in the beautiful Greek islands!","blueprint":{"name":"MIREN","images":["/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca299-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6c5de9c0-a03c-11ee-9209-29ad3ed1d3b4.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca299-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6cf91850-a03c-11ee-9209-29ad3ed1d3b4.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca299-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6da6e480-a03c-11ee-9209-29ad3ed1d3b4.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca299-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6ec8a830-a03c-11ee-9209-29ad3ed1d3b4.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca299-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6fba0d10-a03c-11ee-9209-29ad3ed1d3b4.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca299-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::709e5290-a03c-11ee-9209-29ad3ed1d3b4.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca299-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::72387a90-a03c-